## 10. Sandwich Pattern

```java
public class SandwichPattern {
    public static void main(String[] args) {

        for (int i = 3; i <= 5; i++) {
            for (int j = 1; j <= (6 - i); j++) {
                System.out.print(i + " ");
            }
            System.out.println();
        }

        for (int i = 4; i >= 3; i--) {
            for (int j = 1; j <= (6 - i); j++) {
                System.out.print(i + " ");
            }
            System.out.println();
        }
    }
}
```
